# ğŸ•°ï¸ Terminal Time Machine

> *Ever wished you could rewind time to see exactly what you did in your terminal? Now you can!*

**Terminal Time Machine** records your entire terminal session and replays it later like watching a movie. Perfect for debugging, learning, sharing workflows, or reviewing what you accomplished.

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ¬ **Pixel-perfect playback** - Every character appears exactly when you typed it
- âš¡ **Speed control** - Watch at 0.1x for analysis or 10x for quick reviews  
- ğŸ“Š **Session insights** - Duration, command count, and metrics
- ğŸš€ **Zero overhead** - Lightweight recording

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

```bash
# Install
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/terminal-time-machine
cd terminal-time-machine
cargo build --release

# Record your session
cargo run --bin record
# (Do your work...)
# Press Ctrl+C when done

# Watch it back!
cargo run --bin play
```

